            <span style="display: block; text-transform: uppercase; clear: both; color: #CB2127; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: bold; padding: 0 0 6px; font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif">Error!</span>@msg
